data.text: Enough already. No more hints, no more marketing teases. Either say "yes, we're gong to have a significant LGBTQ character" or own it and say "nah, we're erasing you yet again".
Like Star Wars (multiple times), Star Trek Into the Darkness, Beauty and the Beast, Power Rangers, Thor, Guardians of the Galaxy, Black Panther, Wonder Woman and innumerable others.
